keyMappings:
map <c-o> goBack
map <c-i> goForward
map } scrollPageDown
map { scrollPageUp
map <a-h> LinkHints.activateMode action=hover
map <a-F> LinkHints.activateMode action=focus
map yh LinkHints.activateMode action=copy-text
map s Vomnibar.activate keyword=g
map w Vomnibar.activate keyword=w
map <a-s> Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=g
map <a-w> Vomnibar.activateInNewTab keyword=w
map <a-,> moveTabLeft count=69
map <a-.> moveTabRight count=69
map R reload hard
map J nextTab
map K previousTab
